  04 Jun 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org>
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  Move various kde-base packages to kde-apps.

  25 Aug 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -synaptiks-0.8.1-r2.ebuild,
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  Mark stable on amd64.

  09 Aug 2014; Andreas Schuerch <nativemad@gentoo.org>
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  x86 stable, see bug 489408

  24 Jul 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Punt description for USE="upower" which is close enough to global description;
  as in, the nature of the package will fill in the blank.

  06 Jul 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> synaptiks-0.8.1-r2.ebuild,
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  Clean up obsolete dependencies on virtual/python-argparse and virtual/python-
  unittest2 (those packages were only required for <=python-2.6).

  31 May 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> synaptiks-0.8.1-r2.ebuild,
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  Allow falling back to sys-power/upower-pm-utils.

  14 Mar 2014; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org>
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  Cosmetics.

  15 Dec 2013; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> synaptiks-0.8.1-r2.ebuild,
  synaptiks-0.8.1-r4.ebuild:
  Remove dep on kde-base/kdesdk-scripts by eliasp.

